---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-container">
      <h1>About</h1>

      <div class="bio">
        <p>
          I've spent the last decade-plus as a building energy engineer — auditing hospitals,
          airports, schools, and office towers; commissioning systems; and building tools
          for the people doing that work. Most of that time was focused on monitoring-based
          commissioning (MBCx) and SkySpark analytics.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm in the middle of a transition — still an engineer, increasingly a builder.
          I use AI to build tools I don't have the software background to build otherwise.
          I'm upfront about that. The tools work because I know what needs building;
          the AI handles the parts I don't.
        </p>
        <p>
          <!-- TODO: Expand with full credentials from most recent resume.
               Key items: 2017 ISBD team lead (winning team), conference presentations
               at CxEnergy and ASHRAE, publication in Airport Cooperative Research Program:
               Airport Energy Resiliency Primer and Roadmap.
               Also: career transition narrative from MBCx/SkySpark to developer-adjacent role. -->
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm also writing a novel. <a href="/water-rising">Water Rising</a> is climate
          fiction set in Naples, Florida — about technology, what we choose to do with it,
          and what happens when we get it wrong.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="links">
        <a href="https://github.com/mbcoalson" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mathew-coalson/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="/writing">Writing</a>
        <a href="/tools">Tools</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-container { max-width: 680px; }
  h1 { margin-bottom: var(--space-l); }
  .bio p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }
  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding-top: var(--space-l);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
  }
  .links a {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .links a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }
</style>
